Creating table:

CREATE table users(
	username varchar(30) NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,
	password varchar(30),
	name varchar(30),
	);

Inserting a row into table:

Insert into users (username,password,name)
values(‘ninja’,’bunty2020’,’bunty chauhan’)

2nd method shorthand :
INSERT INTO agents
VALUES ("A001","Jodi","London",.12,"075-1248798");



Clear entry of table without deleting table:
TRUNCATE TABLE Categories;



Deleting a complete table:
DROP TABLE table_name;


Delete a row from table:
DELETE FROM user WHERE username=’ninja’;


Update a cell in table:

UPDATE users
SET password= ‘sachin123’ 
WHERE username=’sachin6174’;
